      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation is subject to version control, regression testing, and documented release procedures consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 used under documented QA procedures including version control, unit testing, and regression test suite. Commercial solver release notes and validation reports confirm compliance with MRL 2 SQA requirements."
