      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental dataset uses standardized blood analogue fluid with documented preparation protocol. Sample-to-sample variability incorporated in reported experimental uncertainty bounds. Formal test sample characterization assessment not required at MRL 2 for comparative hemolysis evaluation."
